				<p>Show your favorites</p>
			</div>
			<div class='form-element grid-70'>
				<p>As far as Favorite Wall goes, you’re done.</p>

				<img src='/images/how-does-this-work/3.jpg' />
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class='grid-100 grid-parent'>
